        "content": "JARVIS 4.5 — Multi-Agent AI Operating Assistant\n\nEntry Points: Telegram | Website Webhook | Local Script\n\nArchitecture:\n  Router + Specialized Agents | Local Device Bridge | Memory System\n\nAgents (9):\n  planner | executor | browser | memory | vision | coding | google | security | scheduler\n\nFlow:\n  Entry → Normalizer → Auth → Rate Limit → Intent Router → [General Chat | Service Dispatcher | Local Bridge] → Response\n\nLocal Device Ops:\n  browser (open, navigate, tabs, screenshot)\n  apps (open, close, restart, focus, list)\n  files (list, read, write, move, copy, delete, search, compress, extract)\n  screen (screenshot, record, OCR)\n  shell (execute with safety)\n  system (info, processes, kill)\n\nEnv: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, GROQ_API_KEY, GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID, GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET, GOOGLE_REFRESH_TOKEN, OWNER_USER_ID, JARVIS_BRIDGE_SECRET",
